snippet.title: Desperate: Vladivostok - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Desperate: Vladivostok is a Bullet-Hell VR action filled game with furious fights and adrenaline shootouts accompanied by dynamic music. Dive into the criminal history of a hired killer in the post-Soviet cyberpunk entourage and fight with him all the way 'til the end.

Releasing Summer 2022 for Meta Quest and PlayStation VR.
